snippet.title: Crimson Skies: High Road to Revenge Playthrough
snippet.description:
There are no subtitles.

Developed by FASA Interactive and published by Microsoft in 2003, Crimson Skies: High Road to Revenge is a arcade flight shooter only released for the Xbox. This is a mostly complete playthrough on hard (which I don't recommend if you want to play this for some casual fun) I believe I did miss a couple of side missions, sorry. 

Intro - 00:00 - 4:20 
Tutorial - 4:20 - 10:51 
A Ship Without a Captain (free roam) - 10:51 - 27:51 
Man Overboard - 27:51 - 42:04
Send 'Em Packing - 42:04 - 51:26 
A Dark Night - 51:26 - 59:57 
A Mine in the Desert (free roam) - 59:57 - 1:32:24
A Desert Mirage - 1:32:24 - 1:47:46
A Gift for the Navajo - 1:47:46 - 1:59:50
Soloho and the Three Trials - 1:59:50 - 2:15:18
The Mystery of the Mine - 2:15:18 - 2:30:07 
A Spider to the Fly - 2:30:07 - 2:42:09
Finding Brooklyn In Chicago (free roam) 2:42:09 - 3:01:55
Jail Break 3:01:55 - 3:13:14 
Payback - 3:13:14 - 3:26:49
The Spider Menace - 3:26:49 - 3:35:32
The Lost City (free roam) - 3:35:32 - 3:53:59
The Puzzle of the Sun Circle (free roam) - 3:53:59 - 4:15:37
Darkness Within - 4:15:37 - 4:46:49
The Windy City 1 - 4:46:49 - 4:51:23
The Windy City 2 - 4:51:23 - 4:58:02
Ending Cutscenes - 4:58:02 - 4:59:00 
Credits - 4:59:00 - 5:02:30
